{
  "name": "Evolution API - Send Media",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🖼️ Evolution API — Send Media\n\n**Goal:** Send images, videos, or documents to WhatsApp via `/message/sendMedia/{instance}`.\n\n**Required body fields:**\n- `mediatype` — `image` | `video` | `document`\n- `mimetype` — e.g. `image/png`, `video/mp4`, `application/pdf`\n- `media` — public URL OR base64 string\n- `fileName` — used especially for documents\n- `caption` — optional text shown with the media\n\n**URL vs base64:**\n- URL is easier but must be **publicly reachable** (Evolution fetches it).\n- base64 works for private files but inflates payload size.",
        "height": 480,
        "width": 420,
        "color": 5
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [-560, -260],
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "note-intro-002",
      "name": "Lesson Note"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {},
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.manualTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [-100, 0],
      "id": "trigger-002",
      "name": "When clicking 'Test workflow'"
    },
    {
